<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_577" id="287v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_577_r2l1">Den von <expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan> vnd wınſheım <expan>cuil<ex>ibet</ex></expan> <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_577_r2l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> eẅch mag eẅr erber <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> dıe <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> ʒu Vlme <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l3">geſagt haben wıe man daſelbs <expan>abgeſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt / <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> . wıe dıe ſtette </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l5">der <expan>v<ex>er</ex>eynung</expan> in ſwoben 
<add><ab facs="#facs_577_r2l4">den andern ſtettebotten </ab></add> am lecʒen ein ſchrıft <expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> geben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l6">haben / vnd wıe Darnach ein ſchrıft vnd . <expan>ratſlagu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> begrıffen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l7">ıſt . von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincʒ ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc / Derſelben <expan>beıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l8">ſchrıft / <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> in dıſem brıef </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l9">
<add><ab facs="#facs_577_r1l1">das wellet bey </ab><ab facs="#facs_577_r1l2">ewch <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> ın </ab><ab facs="#facs_577_r1l3">der <expan>beſte<ex>n</ex></expan> geheim </ab><ab facs="#facs_577_r1l4">ʒu halten . als Jr </ab><ab facs="#facs_577_r1l5">ſelbs auch wol </ab><ab facs="#facs_577_line_1618414562874_38"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mugt / daʒ das gut vnd not ıſt </ab></add> Vnd wenn eẅr erber <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> nehſten ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wırdt . ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l10">wellen wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>verr<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von den <expan>dıng<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt eẅch reden . Denn wo wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l11"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> vincencij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_577" id="287v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von <expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan> und Winsheim
                                <expan>cuil<ex>ibet</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, ewch mag ewr erber
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, die
                            <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> zu Ulme
                            <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> ist, wol gesagt haben, wie man daselbs
                                <expan>abgeschaid<ex>en</ex></expan> ist,
                            <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan> wie die stette der
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>eynung</expan> in Swoben <add>den andern
                            stettebotten</add> am leczen ein schrift <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> geben haben und wie darnach ein schrift und
                                <expan>ratslagu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> begriffen ist von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz sache
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.; derselben
                            <expan>beid<ex>er</ex></expan> schrift <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan> in disem brief. <add>Das wellet bey ewch
                                    <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> in der
                                <expan>beste<ex>n</ex></expan> geheim zu halten, als ir selbs auch
                            wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> mugt, daz das gut und not
                        ist</add>; und wenn ewr erber <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> nehsten zu uns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wirdt, so wellen wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>verr<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von den <expan>ding<ex>en</ex></expan> mit
                        ewch reden. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Vincencii. </ab>
</div>
